+#define ASM_OUTPUT_ALIGN_WITH_NOP(FILE,LOG)                   \
+  do                                                          \
+    {                                                         \
+      if ((LOG) < 3)                                          \
+        {                                                     \
+          ASM_OUTPUT_ALIGN (FILE,LOG);                        \
+        }                                                     \
+      else /* nop == ori r0,r0,0 */                           \
+        fprintf (FILE, "\t.align32 %d,0x60000000\n", (LOG));  \
+    } while (0)
